Version control systems (VCS)
=========================

	Ø It us used to track changes in code
	Ø It remembers every change you make 
	Ø You can go back to any previous version 
	Ø Many people can work on the same project without conflicts 

Git commands
============

	1. Git status
	2. Git add
	3. Git commit
	4. Git push
	5. Git reset
	6. Git revert
	7. Git remote add origin
	8. Git remote -v
	9. Git branch
	10. Git pull
	11. Git branch
	12. Git remote remove origin
	13. Git clone 
	14. Git fork

